Package io.jans.orm.exception

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AuthenticationException
    An exception is a result if user don't have required permissions or failed to authenticate him
    BasePersistenceException
    The base Throwable type for LDAP Mapping.
    EntryDeleteException
    An exception is a result if LDAP entry defined incorrectly.
    EntryPersistenceException
    An exception is a result if LDAP entry defined incorrectly.
    InvalidArgumentException
    An exception is a result of something wrong in input parameters.
    KeyConversionException
    Exception thrown when a dn to key conversion problem occurs
    MappingException
    An exception is a result of something screwy in the O-R mappings.
    PropertyAccessException
    A problem occurred accessing a property of an instance of a persistent class by reflection.
    PropertyNotFoundException
    Indicates that an expected getter or setter method could not be found on a class.
    SearchEntryException
    An exception is a result if search operation fails
    UnsupportedOperationException
    An exception is a result if server doesn't support operation.
